data.message: Is there any guide for getting it into Bootstrap (preferably replacing original button styles not just keeping two versions)?

This file has only the buttons style in bootstrap  so you can change their colors or anything you want :) http://cl.ly/code/0t2x1x1O0L1B otherwise have a look on this page: http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/customize.html you can add the colors your want and generate the bootstrap files
